---
title: Sweet & Spicy Rainbow Edamame Rice Bowls with Cabbage, Carrots & Sesame Dressing
description: You can definitely make a sandwich in 10 minutes, but our chefs heard the call for lighter, more veggie-forward lunches, and present this bowl instead. Get ready to dig into buttery rice beside sweet soy-glazed edamame with just a touch of heat, plus cabbage, carrot, and cucumber salad in a savory sesame dressing. Sprinkle it all with fresh cilantro, and you’ve got an eat-the-rainbow lunch idea we can all feel really good about.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6492ea2a4b18c31a619ff357-0d56d5de.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6492ea2a4b18c31a619ff357.pdf
time required: 10 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-spicy-rainbow-edamame-rice-bowls-6492ea2a4b18c31a619ff357
nutrition:
  calories: 540 kcal
  fat: 21 g
